2


V


∂

S

2





+
r
S



∂
V


∂
S



−
r
V
=
0


{\displaystyle {\frac {\partial V}{\partial t}}+{\frac {1}{2}}\sigma ^{2}S^{2}{\frac {\partial ^{2}V}{\partial S^{2}}}+rS{\frac {\partial V}{\partial S}}-rV=0}



可以簡化為熱力方程：








∂
u


∂
τ



=




∂

2


u


∂

